{
  "stem": "5255.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I didn't have any papers, but I had a paper that I was liberated in Bavaria.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So the Polish guard on the border says, where is your papers?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Oh, I took out a paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I gave him my paper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He says, I can't read that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I figure even if he brings his superior who could read, he can tell that this is not exactly a passport to go to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I left him holding the paper, I turned around, and I jumped up the train that was on the Czechoslovakian side-- Slovakia then, on the Polish frontier.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I locked myself in the toilet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I was sitting there for about an hour until the train left.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in a little while I went-- I was in Prague.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That was the story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Prague, I went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was also an interesting sequel to that, that in Prague the Jewish boys told me what to do.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, now that you're in Prague, go to the Polish consul and tell them that you're on your way to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They'll give you money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They'll give you a lodging in a hotel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they'll give you a permit to stay in Prague for 10 days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And also you'll be able to go to a doctor for an examination at no charge.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to the Polish consul and I told them, I just came from Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm on my way to Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, oh, wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he did exactly what they told me he's going to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he gave me some money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I didn't have the Czechoslovakian kroner they use-- and also food stamps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At that time, they still had food stamps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, it was 1945.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I had all these privileges.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
